augroup scilab
  au!
  " 1;6B is C-S-Down
  au FileType scilab imap [1;6B <Space>..<CR><Space><Space>
  au FileType scilab nmap [1;6B i<Space>..<CR><Space><Space><ESC><ESC>
augroup END

